    "description": "The <tt>AllowTcpForwarding</tt> parameter specifies whether TCP forwarding is permitted.\nTo disable TCP forwarding, add or correct the following line in\n{{{ sshd_config_file() }}}\n<pre>AllowTcpForwarding no</pre>",
